lead_paragraph: Defending champion Anna Karolina Schmiedlova was eliminated from the first round of the Katowice Open on Wednesday, losing to unseeded Pauline Parmentier of France 6-2, 6-0.

headline.print_headline: Defending Champion Schmiedlova Eliminated From Katowice Open
